1052
01:20:19,047 --> 01:20:22,084
Yes, I did.

1053
01:20:22,167 --> 01:20:26,240
- But we haven't heard a thing.
- See what he has to say, Da.

1054
01:20:26,287 --> 01:20:28,721
Go on.

1055
01:20:28,807 --> 01:20:32,959
