1106
01:24:08,247 --> 01:24:11,239
Your trouble is,Joe,
you want to rule the fucking world.

1107
01:24:13,727 --> 01:24:15,160
Paddy's all right.

1108
01:24:26,687 --> 01:24:28,245
Soon, we were all
one happy family.

1109
01:24:28,327 --> 01:24:30,079
Again!

1110
