Even Kojak was ready to forgive.

1111
01:24:33,207 --> 01:24:36,247
- Live and let live.
- Barker began to panic.

1112
01:24:36,247 --> 01:24:39,159
He told us to take our socks
out of the window.

1113
01:24:39,247 --> 01:24:41,841
He thought we were signalling
to other prisoners.

1114
01:24:41,927 --> 01:24:45,158
We're not signalling.
We're drying our socks out.

1115
01:24:45,247 --> 01:24:46,646
- Take the socks out of the window.
- Who says?

1116
01:24:46,727 --> 01:24:47,842
