1123
01:25:12,687 --> 01:25:15,121
Look, you do it your way,
and we'll do it ours, all right?

1124
01:25:15,207 --> 01:25:18,961
- You can read our demands.
- Go back to your cells.

1125
01:25:19,047 --> 01:25:20,685
Blankets!

1126
01:25:21,567 --> 01:25:25,037
- For God's sake, put a stop to this.
- You're weakening my position.

1127
01:25:25,127 --> 01:25:26,924
- It will end in violence.
- Good.

1128
01:25:27,007 --> 01:25:29,316
- What's good about it?
- It's all they understand.

1129
01:25:32,567 --> 01:25:34,319
Barker refused to negotiate.

1130
01:25:34,607 --> 01:25:36,643
But with the screws gone,
we'd a brief taste of freedom.

1131
01:25:36,727 --> 01:25:38,046
Check out Ronnie!

1132
01:25:40,087 --> 01:25:42,237
Him swallow half Africa.

1133
01:25:43,087 --> 01:25:44,884
I give him about an hour.

1134
01:25:51,247 --> 01:25:54,080
We found out later
our protest got on TV.

1135
01:25:54,167 --> 01:25:56,681
And that's when
the riot squad was ordered in.

1136
01:26:11,687 --> 01:26:14,247
