getting down the stairs.

1153
01:27:39,207 --> 01:27:42,247
Well, I'll just have to
go up and see him then.

1154
01:27:42,247 --> 01:27:45,125
- The delegation has seen enough.
- Right-o. Sorry.

1155
01:27:45,207 --> 01:27:48,244
