Is that all right? Sorry.

1156
01:27:48,327 --> 01:27:51,842
I'll meet you outside, okay?
Sorry.

1157
01:27:57,967 --> 01:27:59,446
Sorry, I can't--

1158
01:27:59,527 --> 01:28:01,563
Pulmonary thrombosis.

1159
01:28:01,647 --> 01:28:04,605
- And he's getting proper medication?
- Aye.

1160
01:28:09,287 --> 01:28:10,561
Son?

1161
01:28:13,327 --> 01:28:15,318
That's-- Is it Gerry?

1162
01:28:15,407 --> 01:28:16,806
That's Gerry.

1163
01:28:16,887 --> 01:28:19,606
He's had a spot of bother
with lawyers in the past.

1164
01:28:23,447 --> 01:28:26,359
He's all yours.
Fifteen minutes.

1165
01:28:26,447 --> 01:28:28,244
- Thank you.
- Sit down.

1166
01:28:35,247 --> 01:28:37,238
You wanted to see me, Gerry?

1167
01:28:57,967 --> 01:29:00,640
Why are you giving
my father false hope?

1168
01:29:00,727 --> 01:29:02,399
Sorry?

1169
01:29:02,487 --> 01:29:05,445
